"""Test get_board_stats."""
response = self.perf.get_board_stats(board_id=self.p_data.board_id, metrics
    =pc.KPI, start_time=self.time_now, end_time=self.time_now)
self.assertIsInstance(response, dict)
self.assertEqual(response.get('reporting_level'), self.common.
    convert_to_snake_case(pc.BOARD))
